asset.hookText:
Want to spend a day in the studio with Plan B?  we're giving you the chance to hang out with Plan B and create your very own track with his help.
you've got 400 words to tell us why Plan B should choose you, as well as sending a link to your facebook, myspace, website or blog so he can hear what you do.
